OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782895707
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment shoplifter
OL,4,Cdetained by off-duty officer
OL,6,FAn off duty Kent Police officer
OL,7,Fstepped in to help staff after a
OL,8,Fshoplifting incident in Gillingham.
OL,10,FAt around 3.50pm on Monday 8 June
OL,11,F2026, PC Alice O'Brien was filling up
OL,12,Fher car at a petrol station on
OL,13,FBeechings Way when she noticed an
OL,14,Faltercation taking place.
OL,16,FNicholas Noble had entered the petrol
OL,17,Fstation and began placing items,
OL,18,Fincluding: Solero ice lollies, a
OL,19,FSnickers ice cream bar, Mini Milk
OL,20,Flollies and bacon into a carrier bag.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
