OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782895707
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment shoplifter
OL,4,Cdetained by off-duty officer
OL,6,FAttempting to leave the shop, a staff
OL,7,Fmember confronted Noble, 45, leading
OL,8,Fto a struggle over the bag.
OL,10,FPC O'Brien stated she was an off duty
OL,11,Fofficer and began assisting the
OL,12,Femployee.
OL,14,FDuring the minute long effort, another
OL,15,Fmember of the public removed a knife
OL,16,Ffrom Noble's waistband.
OL,18,FPC O'Brien's colleague was on duty at
OL,19,Fthe time and, with the man subdued,
OL,20,Fshe called him to request assistance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782895707
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment shoplifter
OL,4,Cdetained by off-duty officer
OL,6,FNoble, of Hazlemere Drive, Gillingham,
OL,7,Fwas arrested for shoplifting and
OL,8,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,10,FAt Medway Magistrates' Court on
OL,11,FTuesday 16 June 2026, he pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to all charges and a further
OL,13,Fcount of resisting an officer in their
OL,14,Fduty.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced to six months in
OL,17,Fprison, with a further six added for a
OL,18,Fseparate case totalling 12 months'
OL,19,Fimprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782895707
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment shoplifter
OL,4,Cdetained by off-duty officer
OL,6,FPC O'Brien said: "I did what any of my
OL,7,Fcolleagues would do, which is help
OL,8,Fmembers of the public who are in
OL,9,Fpotential danger.
OL,11,F"When I saw them get violent, I knew I
OL,12,Fhad to step in. The staff member and
OL,13,Fmember of public who assisted were
OL,14,Fabsolute superstars, and I'm so lucky
OL,15,Fone of them spotted and removed the
OL,16,Fknife otherwise the incident could
OL,17,Fhave had far more serious consequences.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782895707
OL,3,CCCTV captures moment shoplifter
OL,4,Cdetained by off-duty officer
OL,6,F"Learning afterwards that he had a
OL,7,Fprevious conviction made me even more
OL,8,Fglad that I got involved and we
OL,9,Fmanaged to hold him there until he
OL,10,Fcould be formally arrested.
OL,12,F"The Medway community and its
OL,13,Fbusinesses are safer now that Noble is
OL,14,Fbehind bars."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
